Vehement:


Vehement looked to Destructor, and the direction KitKat's comm. transmission 
was coming from.
Not very bright, he thought.  I'm with her own forces and she's asking me to 
deactivate the autogun...unless this bot in front of me is lying...

Vehement activated his forearm computer's comm. unit.  "Your leader is here." 
Vehement said to Destructor.

"KitKat, this is Vehement.  Defenses are on hold, it is safe to come to my 
location and talk."
